{"tid":537213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九鐵80年代電氣化火車傳聞將會拆毀","createTime":"2018-01-22T13:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T13:56:55.000Z","uid":10540,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d912320db133c3cfd279c8cc3a9ed1513e115836","tid":537213,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"from:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abandonedhkre/photos/a.1753705071563582.1073741967.1470425696558189/1974981222769298/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabandonedhkre%2Fphotos%2Fa.1753705071563582.1073741967.1470425696558189%2F1974981222769298%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=k3FtystjW27N0V0sEM17sp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9eb71f45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abandonedhkre/photos/a.1753705071563582.1073741967.1470425696558189/1974981222769298/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/media/blog/files/501/501668/2016/10/501668_1477847243721.jpg?t=d02d98366d5cf682c16de42e7161d726%22\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Fmedia%2Fblog%2Ffiles%2F501%2F501668%2F2016%2F10%2F501668_1477847243721.jpg%3Ft%3Dd02d98366d5cf682c16de42e7161d726%2522&h=b254fddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26814813_1974981222769298_9015917344082604808_n.jpg?oh=369a1ba53fce3e16322acd8a5e28ffd3&amp;oe=5AE98086\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26814813_1974981222769298_9015917344082604808_n.jpg%3Foh%3D369a1ba53fce3e16322acd8a5e28ffd3%26oe%3D5AE98086&h=3bc13607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此刻無價<br />\n<br />\n能夠喺現代時空登上屬於過去嘅頭等車廂，一圓細個想搭黃頭頭等嘅夢，坐一坐灰色皮櫈，感覺真係好似坐左時光機一樣，好想呢一刻可以定格，享受多一陣。可惜每1分鐘便有60秒過去，但至少我哋蒞過坐過，完夢了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳聞閒置多時嘅黃頭近有被移入何東樓係為進行測試作準備，測試過後將會拆毀此車。收到呢個消息，真係好灰鳩，呢抽黃頭最後都係逃唔出灰飛煙滅嘅命運。</strong>到呢度，腦入面響起：<br />\n<br />\n這個剎那宇宙 拒絕永久<br />\n世事無常還是未看夠 還未看透"},{"pid":"645e2696963081aad7a9943e7aefc37404652595","tid":537213,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06974ee0fe733a9fdbf7bc5100abdf084ee9e7ee","tid":537213,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"有巴膠成架退役巴士都買到，鐵膠買唔到?"},{"pid":"64e71a912f8d79c1cbd1c8b0dc82ca0e532ce5c4","tid":537213,"uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06974ee0fe733a9fdbf7bc5100abdf084ee9e7ee","tid":537213,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"有巴膠成架退役巴士都買到，鐵膠買唔到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"巴士可以汨露天停車場<br />\n火車可以放係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a3dd28803c861b181f0166c44b90b3952f0897","tid":537213,"uid":46752,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"64e71a912f8d79c1cbd1c8b0dc82ca0e532ce5c4","tid":537213,"uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06974ee0fe733a9fdbf7bc5100abdf084ee9e7ee","tid":537213,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"有巴膠成架退役巴士都買到，鐵膠買唔到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"巴士可以汨露天停車場<br />\n火車可以放係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"露天停車場"},{"pid":"f97af762e005c427da67509083394d8f71f544e4","tid":537213,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c2366c2f2676352890b055f3dd7227eefd472c","tid":537213,"uid":31098,"like":3,"dislike"